title: Lured, trapped, forever marked - a Queensland story
text:
Lured, trapped, forever marked - a Qu... Lured, trapped, forever marked - a Queensland story 1 hr ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
A man who was lured into a homosexual encounter with a police officer in Cairns in 1988 then charged with aggravated sexual assault says the conviction "never, ever goes away". The moment Alan Raabe's eyes locked with another man's on the Cairns foreshore his childhood dreams, and life as he planned it, were over.   Sydney Morning Herald.
